## CONSTRAINTS
- Bedrock: invoke via APAC inference PROFILE:
    apac.anthropic.claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022-v2:0
- Bedrock budget: max 50 invocations + 20,000 tokens per learner per session.
- Bedrock HARD COST GUARD (env vars on bedrock-enrich Lambda):
    BEDROCK_MAX_INVOCATIONS = 38
    BEDROCK_MAX_TOKENS      = 18000
- Bedrock FORBIDDEN: Studio, Knowledge Bases, Agents, AgentCore.
- Lambda: max 10 functions per learner; max 2048 MB memory; runtime python3.12.
- SageMaker: max 1 endpoint; serverless only on D9; NO GPU.
- Glue: max 3 jobs (type=glueetl); max 4 DPU per job; max 6 DPU-h cumulative.
- DynamoDB: PAY_PER_REQUEST billing.
- Kinesis: 2 shards per stream (sandbox default).
- Step Functions: 256 KiB execution state limit. NEVER pass rows[] through state.
- Athena: workgroup `accelya_<learner>` enforces BytesScannedCutoffPerQuery (100 MB).
- GitHub: public starter repo; MRs only.

