## EXAMPLES
- Cancellation envelope (input to producer):
    { event_id, event_type: 'cancellation', event_time, ingest_time,
      airline_code: 'AI', booking_date: '2026-05-09', pnr: '6X7Y8Z',
      source_system: 'GDS',
      payload: { pnr, cancel_reason_code: 'WX', cancellation_event_id } }
- Enriched record (output of state machine):
    { ...envelope,
      enrichment: { sentiment: 'neutral', priority: 'normal', summary: '...' }
                   OR null (sampled out OR budget guard fired),
      sampled: true | false,
      enriched_at: '<iso8601>',
      consumer_seq: '<sequence_number>',
      consumer_shard: 'shardId-000000000000',
      sfn_execution_arn: '...' }
- Idempotency claim (stream_seen_keys table):
    PK 'stream#accelya-bookings-stream-<learner>#shardId-000000000000#<seq>'
    Item: { pk, status: 'CLAIMED|IN_PROGRESS|COMPLETED', claimed_at, ttl }
- Stream-state DDB table:
    stream_seen_keys_<learner>: stream/event idempotency
    consumer_state_<learner>:   Day-10 dynamic sample_rate (NEW)
- ASL state names (inference-pipeline.asl.json):
    BedrockEnrich (Task) → Persist (Task)
                        ↘ Quarantine (Pass) on States.ALL catch
